        <p>@Localizer["Collect treasures through your adventures, make of the barter or give of your person in local missions. And maybe that the wealth will smile to you!"]</p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-4" style="text-align: center;">
        <img alt="Gold" src="~/images/Game/logo.svg" style="height: 140px;">
        <h3>@Localizer["Experience an adventure!"]</h3>
        <p>@Localizer["Discover a living universe, where you're writings matter. Experience epic adventures in this world of conflict and terror."]</p>
